snippet.title: The World Ends With You: Noise Busters - Neku Gameplay
snippet.description:
The World Ends With You: Noise Busters
A Score-Attack arcade game based on the cult classic, The World Ends With You.
============================================
Members of ICU Gigasoft Forums interested in Beta testing the project, please head to the forums!
============================================
http://icugigasoft.freeforums.org/ (Forums)
http://udivision.blogspot.com (Blog)

Note: This is just a free fan game.  Square Enix owns "The World Ends With You", and all related properties. Buy the mobile version of the game to support- OH WAIT, THEY REMOVED IT.  :-(
